import React, { Component } from 'react'
import {  Image, Label, Segment, Container, Card,Input, Form,Icon, Message } from 'semantic-ui-react'

class Bio extends Component {
  render() {
    return (
        <Container>
           <Card.Group itemsPerRow='4'>
           <Card>
      <Card.Content>
        <Card.Header content='Jake Smith' />
        <Card.Meta content='' />
        <Card.Description content='Jake is a drummer living in New York.' />
      </Card.Content>
    </Card>

    <Card>
      <Card.Content>
        <Card.Header content='Jake Smith' />
        <Card.Meta content='' />
        <Card.Description content='Jake is a drummer living in New York.' />
      </Card.Content>
    </Card>

    <Card>
      <Card.Content
        header='Elliot Baker'
        meta='Friend'
        description='Elliot is a music producer living in Chicago.'
      />
    </Card>

    <Card
      header='Jenny Hess'
      meta='Friend'
      description='Jenny is a student studying Media Management at the New School'
    />
  </Card.Group>


</Container>
    )
  }
}
export default Bio;
